\begin_layout Subsection
SP3 Battery Care
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Surface is designed to work between 32°F and 95°F (or 0°C to 35°C).
 Lithium-ion batteries are sensitive to high temperatures, so keep your
 Surface out of the sun and don’t leave it in a hot car.
 The battery doesn’t need to be empty or low before you recharge.
 You can recharge the battery whenever you’d like.
 However, it’s best to let the battery run to below 10 percent at least
 once per month before you recharge it.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
How to make battery last
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
