\begin_layout Section
10.25 sRGB color space
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(interested in its transformation)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Review high school biology knowledge
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
DNA, RNA, Gene relationship
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Dominant Gene, 基因座（locus）,等位基因（allele）,基因座在基因组中的排列位置称为基因图谱（genetic map），基因作图（Gen
e mapping）则是测定基因座与特定性状关系的过程。二倍体与多倍体细胞的某些染色体上，在同一基因座上有相同的等位基因，这类细胞称为纯合子/同型合子（homo
zygous）。若是相同基因座上含有不同的等位基因，则称作杂合子/异型合子（heterozygous）。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
\color red
phenotype
\emph default
\color inherit
: 表型.对于一个生物而言，表示它某一特定的物理外观或成分。一个人是否有耳珠、植物的高度、人的血型、蛾的颜色等等，都是表型的例子。 
\color blue
表型主要受生物的基因型和环境影响，表型可分为连续变异或不连续变异的。前者较易受环境因素影响，基因型上则会受多个等位基因影响，如体重、智力和身高；后者仅受几个等位
基因影响，而且很少会被环境改变，如血型、眼睛颜色和卷舌的能力。对于不连续变异，若有两个生物表现型相同，其基因型未必一样，这是因为其中一方可能有隐性基因。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Q: what is gene expression level?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
10.26 Spacemacs ESS loading problem fixed on Windows 10
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Spacemacs ESS loading problem
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Previously, spacemacs was unable to detect the .R extension file so that
 ess mode was not enabled for the R script files.
 Tonight, by comparing the versions of ess package loaded by spacemacs on
 my Y410p Win 10 & SP3 Win 10 via the command 
\color red

\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

M-x ess-version
\color inherit

\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

, I found that though the ess 15.09 version was installed on my Y410p Win
 10, the version shown in spacemacs is 15.03, which is an older version.
 
\emph on
\color blue
Then I realized the emacs I installed on Y410p Win 10 OS is a modified version
 with ess already installed in the emacs folder, this might be the cause
 of the problem.

\emph default
\color inherit
 So I uninstalled the modified version and installed an almost unmodified
 version and re-git-clone the spacemacs folder from github.
 Now, everything familiar features with ESS mode are back again!
\end_layout

\begin_layout Chapter
November
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
11.9 Finally succesfully installed Spacemacs on my MBP
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
All problem solved after I modify the permission access of the /Users/chuanliu/
 directory.
 Actually, it suffice to modify the permission for /Users/chuanliu/.emacs.d/
 directory.
 Note that the cause for this problem is when I use git to clone the spacemacs
 .emac.d directory from github, I use the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

sudo git clone
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 command which render the ownership of the .emacs.d to be root so that when
 I first open emacs, it kept telling me it has no permision to create directorie
s like .cache/ and elpa/ etc.
 
\emph on
\color red
So be careful when you add the sudo to a command.
\end_layout

